<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Football News Website</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

<style>

body{
font-family: Arial;
margin:0;
background:#f2f2f2;
}

header{
background:#0a3d62;
color:white;
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
}

nav{
background:#1e3799;
padding:10px;
text-align:center;
position:sticky;
top:0;
}

nav a{
color:white;
margin:10px;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:bold;
}

nav a:hover{
color:yellow;
}

section{
padding:40px;
background:white;
margin:20px;
border-radius:8px;
}

.news{
margin-bottom:20px;
padding:15px;
background:#f9f9f9;
border-radius:8px;
}

footer{
background:#0a3d62;
color:white;
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
}

input,textarea{
width:100%;
padding:10px;
margin:10px 0;
}

button{
padding:10px 20px;
background:#1e3799;
color:white;
border:none;
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<header>
<h1>⚽ Football News Hub</h1>
<p>Latest Football News, Transfers & Live Scores</p>
</header>

<nav>
<a href="#home">Home</a>
<a href="#news">News</a>
<a href="#livescore">Live Scores</a>
<a href="#transfers">Transfers</a>
<a href="#about">About</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
<a href="#privacy">Privacy</a>
</nav>

<section id="home">
<h2>Home</h2>
<p>Welcome to our football news website. Here you will find the latest football news, live scores and transfer updates.</p>
</section>

<section id="news">
<h2>Football News</h2>

<div class="news">
<h3>Champions League Big Match</h3>
<p>The top European clubs will face each other tonight in a thrilling Champions League match.</p>
</div>

<div class="news">
<h3>Young Player Breaks Record</h3>
<p>A young football star has scored 20 goals this season and is becoming very popular.</p>
</div>

</section>

<section id="livescore">
<h2>Live Scores</h2>
<p>Manchester City 2 - 1 Liverpool</p>
<p>Barcelona 3 - 0 Atletico Madrid</p>
<p>Real Madrid 1 - 1 PSG</p>
</section>

<section id="transfers">
<h2>Transfer News</h2>
<p>Several top players are expected to move clubs this summer transfer window.</p>
<p>Rumors suggest big transfers in Premier League and La Liga.</p>
</section>

<section id="about">
<h2>About Us</h2>
<p>This website shares football news, live match updates and transfer rumors from around the world.</p>
</section>

<section id="contact">
<h2>Contact Us</h2>

<form>
<input type="text" placeholder="Your Name">
<input type="email" placeholder="Your Email">
<textarea placeholder="Your Message"></textarea>
<button type="submit">Send</button>
</form>

</section>

<section id="privacy">
<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
<p>This website respects your privacy. We do not share personal information with third parties.</p>
</section>

<footer>
<p>© 2026 Football News Hub</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
